description.0: Warlock and Pip save Silver Surfer from Thor, and must continue to subdue the insane god after the attack!
description.4: Scarlet Witch's involvement in cyberspace thickens, as she and Pixil are captured by a creature of the Cess. Will the Witch be able to rid herself of this techno-nightmare? Werewolf by Night Jack Russell continues to battle Lilin on Halloween night, while Morbius the Vampire embraces a bloodlust.
description.6: Dealing with the Snakeroot and their plans to unleash a virus was difficult enough, but now the sinister symbiote Venom makes his move!
description.7: The creature known as Bi-Beast has destructive plans for Earth, and only Hulk can stop him! And he's got help too - from his cousin Jen, the She-Hulk!
description.8: The invincible Iron Man faces Ultimo-in his deadliest form ever! Can the Armored Avengers survive the Doomsday machine?
description.9: Siege of Darkness cross-over! Doctor Strange attempts to separate the Midnight Sons from the soul of Lilith, but may be overpowered by the task. Jack Russell, Werewolf by Night, has a ghoulish Halloween adventure. But instead of getting candy, Russell's getting decapitated heads! Scarlet Witch gets dragged into cyberspace! The Devil Slayer encounters impish demons getting in the way of a stiff drink.
description.11: Adam Warlock and his Infinity Watch join Asgard's efforts in taking out a rogue Thor!
description.13: Multiple Man suffers an identity crisis and Polaris attempts to help. Radha Dastoor, A.K.A. Haven, offers a disturbing, messianic prophecy for humankind.
description.14: It's all hands on deck (yes, even Wolverine) for Alpha Flight's final battle against the Goddess!
description.15: Prison break - fantastic style! Susan, Johnny, and Ben stage a daring escape from their captors, but can they survive...with an entire Skrull world against them?
description.21: When the Assassins decide they're going to take a sacred Tithe ceremony into their own hands (and pockets!), Gambit's brother Henri LeBeau is caught in the crosshairs. Will Gambit avenge his brother...or become the next ceremonial sacrifice?
description.23: See the stunning origin of Spider-Woman and how Julia Carpenter became a hero.
description.24: Nomad beats the Six Pack at their own game, when he steals an experimental prototype from NASA!
description.26: Into the cosmos! The Secret Defenders face off against the menace of Nebula! Guest-starring Nova, the Human Rocket!
description.27: Wolverine and The Punisher team up against Damage and the Kingpin to put an end to his merciless killing. Defeated, Kingpin must now face Donald Pierce!
description.30: The Jury has Spider-Man pinned between a rock and a hard place, leaving our hero vulnerable to confess. Will Spider-Man be unmasked? Aunt May's investigation into Peter's parents stalls.
description.31: The identity of the enigmatic Mr. Tolliver- revealed! A Sinister rendezvous leads to the return of a deadly foe! And Cable faces a twofold ambush- of his body AND mind!
description.32: Introducing one of the biggest nut jobs Captain America has ever faced! Is anyone ready for Blistik?
description.35: The second part to 'What if the Avengers had lost Operation Storm'. The Earth may be dying, but its heroes will continue to fight for its future.
description.37: The Midnight Sons team with Doctor Strange as the "Siege of Darkness" hits the Sanctum Sanctorum!
description.38: Matt Murdock's connection with Elektra grows stronger. But is Murdock in over his head?
description.42: Daimon may be in for a reunion with ""Dad!"" It's off to Hell for Hellstorm, accompanied by a host of lost souls!
description.44: Logan joins Namor the Sub-Mariner, Ka-Zar, Shanna, and Zabu in battling the Conservator…
description.48: An Infinity Crusade tie-in guest-starring Spider-Man! Moon Knight is deployed by the Goddess to put the kibosh on the wall-crawler!
description.49: Firelord turns up the heat against Nova in the battle for the fate of the Corps!
description.52: When the peaceful solution fails, Modon Kira gathers the Beast Lords from across Onderon to attack Iziz.
description.59: The death of an Avenger! It's the end of an era for the Avengers West Coast.
description.63: The Snakeroot's plan comes to a head! What do they hope to accomplish by kidnapping a cyborg S.H.I.E.L.D. agent and stealing a man-made virus? The answers involve someone close to Daredevil, and will shake his world to its very core!
description.64: Hulk vs. S.H.I.E.L.D.! Both sides appear to be evenly matched, but the Hulk has a trump card up his sleeve. There's one thing Nick Fury can't resist - secret, shocking information, and the Hulk's got it!
description.65: Tony Stark making a fast recovery gets back to his roots, well to his lab, where he makes all of his awesome armored suits! Plus: the first appearance of H.O.M.E.R.!
description.68: Sif and Beta Ray Bill plead with Thor to see reason...but the Thunder God is too far gone under the Valkyrie's spell!
description.70: Forge and Havok come to blows over X-Factor's response to Genosha. A gruesome rescue mission at the Kennedy Center pushes to the team to their breaking point, while Polaris contemplates a new, hopeful landscape for mutantkind following an attempt on her life.
description.72: The unthinkable has happened...Reed Richards is no more. The Fantastic Four are now...the Fantastic Three!? How will Susan, Johnny, and Ben cope with the loss of their beloveed Reed while trying to avert a Skrull invasion?
description.73: In Colorado, Archangel and Jean Grey encounter a mysteriously-revived Candy Southern and Archangel's nemesis Cameron Hodge!
description.79: The first part of this What If? special explores what would have happened if the Avengers had lost Operation: Galactic Storm. Many lose their lives from both sides of the Kree-Shi'ar War.
description.82: Matt Murdock hunts the men that killed his father.
description.85: Julia Carpenter is Spider-Woman and as a member of the Avengers West Coast, she's had to face the villainous group known as Deathweb. When they coming calling for a rematch, can Spider-Woman take on the whole team by herself?
description.88: If it's power you want, this latest team of Secret Defenders is for you! The mystical mastery of DOCTOR STRANGE! The hammer and lightning of THUNDERSTRIKE! The no-holds-barred firepower of WAR MACHINE! The unbridled cosmic might of the SILVER SURFER! What could possibly stand against such a powerful and heroic team? Trust me, you DON'T want to know!
description.89: Following through on his plans to tarnish The Punisher's reputation, Kingpin uses his agent Damage to impersonate Frank and kill innocent civilians.
description.92: The Xandarians, and Queen Adora, call for Nova at their sides in Part Two of “The Starlost.”
description.97: Spider-Man's on trial! But what's his crime? The cybernetic Jury has captured Spidey and is holding him responsible for the release of Venom's symbiote! Aunt May confirms her suspicions about Peter's parents.
description.98: The Sentinel of Liberty battles one his own! Can Captain America defeat Nomad in order to save the life of Slug?

0.text: Warlock and Pip save Silver Surfer from Thor, and must continue to subdue the insane god after the attack!

1.text: Miguel O’ Hara learns the laws of reality don’t exist in Interspace. Gabe O’Hara discovers a shocking development with his girlfriend Kasey. And Net Prophet shows the full range of his reality-warping powers. Will Spider-Man finally escape Interspace?

2.text: With S.H.I.E.L.D and the Avengers deployed to Genosha, it seems that Cortez's plans have failed. With the appearance of a dangerous and powerful stranger however, things may not go the way the Avengers may hope. Is he friend of foe?

3.text: Moondragon and Adam try to cure Maxam of his amnesia...unsuccessfully.

4.text: Scarlet Witch’s involvement in cyberspace thickens, as she and Pixil are captured by a creature of the Cess. Will the Witch be able to rid herself of this techno-nightmare? Note: this issues contains only the Scarlet Witch story.

9.text: Scarlet Witch gets dragged into cyberspace! Note: this issue only contains the Scarlet Witch story.

10.text: A.R.M.S. suffers a dastardly theft! The culprit…Iron Fist!? Why would the heroic Danny Rand suddenly become a thief? It's up to Spidey to find out!

16.text: Beast, Xavier and USAgent defend themselves against the Genoshan Magistrates. Meanwhile, Sersi and Exodus battle it out while Quicksilver and Jean Grey look for a way into Genosha's capitol to save Luna from Cortez's clutches.

17.text: Having had the Adamantium ripped from his skeleton, Logan has left the X-Men to rediscover himself. With his healing factor greatly reduced, Lady Deathstrike takes this moment to make her return!

18.text: Revanche is infected with the Legacy Virus!

19.text: Spider-Man and Shroud go up against the Screaming Masks of Cytorrak! Plus: A very special J. Jonah Jameson story!

20.text: Adam Warlock and Silver Surfer enlist the help of Doctor Strange to take down the mad Thor.

22.text: The Avengers fight for eight millennia of time…right alongside Kang the Conqueror! Former foe becomes ally, as Earth's Mightiest and Kang battle Alioth, Master of all timespans! Don’t miss this pulse pounding conclusion to the Terminatrix Objective!

23.text: See the stunning origin of Spider-Woman and how Julia Carpenter became a hero.

24.text: Nomad beats the Six Pack at their own game, when he steals an experimental prototype from NASA!

25.text: Woden, son of Thor, may be Asgard's only chance to turn the tide against Loki's invasion!

26.text: Into the cosmos! The Secret Defenders face off against the menace of Nebula! Guest-starring Nova, the Human Rocket!

27.text: Wolverine and The Punisher team up against Damage and the Kingpin to put an end to his merciless killing. Defeated, Kingpin must now face Donald Pierce!

28.text: When Mort gets challenged by the “cool kid” in school to race his dad’s car, Mort crashes the car into a train and dies. He then meets Teen Death, the Grim Reaper’s son, and mayhem ensues.

29.text: It's finally time for some honest-to-goodness "Star Wars," as Luke Skywalker and Vrad Dodonna head for a climactic showdown in space with Darth Vader. Meanwhile, the rest of the Rebel Alliance struggles against time to evacuate Yavin Base for their new home on Hoth, as Darth Vader and the Imperial forces plan for a major strike on the Rebel moon. Luke, however, suspects that Vrad is a traitor to the Rebel cause, which leads to an exciting confrontation, as well as a startling turn of events for one of our Rebel heroes!

33.text: Arcade insists that Shatterstar must play his "game" of fighting another hero to the death- but who could his other captive be? Meanwhile, Warpath admits his true feelings to Siryn! How will she take it?

39.text: A high-level meeting of mobster family heads proves an irresistable target for Frank. He rigs the otherwise empty building with explosives and, with his hand on the dead man's switch, takes down everybody but one gangster. The man tries to bargain with Frank, saying they could both walk out. Seconds later, BOOM.

40.text: When Junkpile returns to Las Vegas having captured two X-Men and Xi'an's cocoon, the other X-Men begin a reconnaissance mission!

41.text: All the top UK heroes in one book! Dark Angel and the UK heroes fight it out with the Leader's bodyguards while Death's Head II and Motormouth try to rescue Killpower and Liger.

43.text: What's Mystique planning and why is she impersonating Gambit?

45.text: V.I.G.I.L. takes aim at Punisher after their funding is threatened for failing to come up with any major arrests. Lt. Blackwell blames one man: Frank Castle. The Punisher must escape a web of smugglers and an organization with a vendetta against him.

46.text: Venom wakes up to a strange being attempting to merge with him after being exposed to a vat of ‘sentient' mercury. Eddie's growing relationship with Beck is threatened by his rogue symbiote.

47.text: United by nothing but their HATRED for one man and their thirst for POWER, murderous individuals band together to further their twisted goals. And they will let NOTHING stand in their way! Stan Lee presents the finale of...The Lethal Foes of Spider-Man!

50.text: The Corps of Four conclude their takedown of Demonstaff! But not before learning the truth behind his descent into madness!

51.text: The final fate of Louise Hastings at the hands of…Morbius?! Ghost Rider guest stars!

53.text: The conclusion is here! One by one, stars in the Milky Way galaxy have begun to explode. Can the heroes save the universe? What role will Thanos come to play in the final act?
The conclusion is here! One by one, stars in the Milky Way galaxy have begun to explode. Can the heroes save the universe? What role will Thanos come to play in the final act?

55.text: It's the final showdown between Deadpool and Weapon X in Nepal!

56.text: Tyler Stone and Spider-Man under the will of Thanatos! What devious plans will Thanatos set into motion when he breaks into Alchemax’s Virtual Unreality Lab? And who is the mysterious figure from the Interspace Portal? Spider-Man vs. Thanatos in the Interspace!

57.text: Fans love to see their heroes win, but when the usually unflappable characters lose-when they suffer-readers can't help but devour the story. Wolvie's adamantium removed by Magneto, this issue deals with the horrific aftermath.

58.text: Things go from bad to worse when it is discovered that Cortez has assassinated the Genoshan government!  And who do the Avengers and X-Men factor in?

59.text: The death of an Avenger! It's the end of an era for the Avengers West Coast.

74.text: Working against the clock, the X-Men fly to Genosha to help Xavier. During the journey Colossus must make a difficult decision concerning where his loyalties lie. Meanwhile, Xavier and Beast must bide their time by fighting against new enemies.

75.text: Tombstone takes out anyone and everyone foolish enough to get in his way -- EVEN SPIDER-MAN!

76.text: Silver Surfer must break up a brawl between an entirely insane Thor and Beta Ray Bill!

77.text: Henry Gyrich tests Feral's patience with his blatant hatred of mutants. Will Feral set their differences aside and let Gyrich live to see another day?

80.text: Quasar and the newly-appeared Geometer battle.

81.text: With the help of Kyllian’s staff, Strange finds Iskelior’s pocket dimension while Lilith breaks down its dimensional barriers!

84.text: No matter where the Avengers time-leap, lethal time-trooper robots are on the assault! Terminatrix is up to no good in the Temple of Immortus- the fabric of time and space is in the balance, and only Kang the Conqueror’s return may save the universe.

85.text: Julia Carpenter is Spider-Woman and as a member of the Avengers West Coast, she's had to face the villainous group known as Deathweb. When they coming calling for a rematch, can Spider-Woman take on the whole team by herself?

86.text: The Thing and Human Torch assist Cage in freeing himself of the Bogeyman!

87.text: Loki's malevolent siege of Asgard begins!

88.text: If it's power you want, this latest team of Secret Defenders is for you! The mystical mastery of DOCTOR STRANGE! The hammer and lightning of THUNDERSTRIKE! The no-holds-barred firepower of WAR MACHINE! The unbridled cosmic might of the SILVER SURFER! What could possibly stand against such a powerful and heroic team? Trust me, you DON'T want to know!

89.text: Following through on his plans to tarnish The Punisher's reputation, Kingpin uses his agent Damage to impersonate Frank and kill innocent civilians.

90.text: We all know Venom is a bit insane but in this story, he is LITERALLY going insane…with his personality split in two! A trippy tale told by Daredevil master scribe Ann Nocenti!

91.text: The Web-Slinger is alone against seven of his deadliest foes. Win or lose, one thing is certain…Spidey's not getting out of this one unscathed.

93.text: After Eric takes on the mantle of Thunderstrike, the one true Thor makes the Corps four on a multi-dimensional quest to rescue the wife of Dargo's arch-foe, Demonstaff!

94.text: The true lineage of Vicki Montesi revealed! Vicki taps into the power of the Darkhold to bring Nash back from the brink of death…but at what cost to her eternal soul?

96.text: With the help of their new allies, the Mon Calamari, the Rebels battle the monstrous sea worms of Daluuj. Meanwhile, Darth Vader is cutting a swath of destruction toward the Rebel base on Yavin where Luke Skywalker and General Dodonna's son Vrad prepare for a suicide mission!

99.text: Jack is captured by Faustus and Cap is hot on the trail to free his friend.
